<br>
I think that many of these should happen live on TV, for children to watch with their parents.<br>
<br>
I believe it would cement the idea in young minds that if you commit crimes like this, you get executed.  It is sad that people are imprisoned/executed when innocent, but we aren't helping our society by letting people off with a slap on the risk.  what good is a threat, if everyone knows you won't follow through?<br>
<br>
In medieval times hordes of people used to show up for hangings, children included.  you knew the consequences of your actions.  How much crime is there in the middle east?  under islamic law, the penalties for stealing, rape, murder, and most other crimes are clearly spelled out, and clearly carried out.<br>
<br>
Executions live on TV.  i believe in the future, we'll need fewer of them.<br>
